sentences: David Wali Rahmaan Ebn Hassan Bullard, better known by his stage name Orko Eloheim (formerly Orko the Sycotik Alien) (born 1975/1976) is an American alternative hip hop artist from San Diego, California.
Orko grew up in Encanto, San Diego, where he first started recording his own music in the mid 1980s.
